# Block validation pipeline: header+body+sig as gating function.
*validate(header_ok as i64, body_ok as i64, sig_ok as i64) returns i64
    if header_ok equals 0
        return 1
    if body_ok equals 0
        return 2
    if sig_ok equals 0
        return 3
    0

*main
    log validate(1, 1, 1)
    log validate(1, 0, 1)
    log validate(0, 1, 1)
